0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezo-79-million-mansion-indian-creek-lawsuit-leo-kryss-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2479%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20adjacent%20mansions%20in%20Indian%20Creek%2C%20Florida.%20He'd%20go%20onto%20purchase%20a%20third%20mansion%20on%20the%20island%2C%20which%20he%20secured%20for%20%2490%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20rise%20together%2C%20and%20we%20sink%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ba07cfd-fa62-4866-a7f5-e5493a12badf%5C%22%3EThe%20Bezos%20Effect%20is%20changing%20South%20Florida's%20pricing%20landscape%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELongtime%20Seattle%20resident%20Jeff%20Bezos%20announced%20in%202023%20that%20he%20was%20leaving%20the%20West%20Coast%20and%20heading%20to%20Florida%20%E2%80%94%20following%20the%20trend%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-leaving-california-new-york-moving-florida-texas-reasons-effects-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewealthy%20elites%20seeking%20solace%20in%20the%20Sunshine%20State%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Bezos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6750e4908fbb2783ed2fd31b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222518%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Bezos%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%2C%20whose%20net%20worth%20is%20%24233.7%20billion%20as%20of%20January%202024%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes%2C%20didn't%20buy%20just%20one%20home%20in%20Florida%3B%20he%20bought%20several.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20homes%20are%20located%20on%20a%20secluded%20island%20called%20Indian%20Creek%2C%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-bunker-miami-bezos-tom-brady-ivanka-trump-security-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBillionaire%20Bunker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20good%20reason.%20The%20island%20has%20security%20patrolling%20the%20perimeter%2024%2F7%2C%20so%20unwelcomed%20visitors%20%E2%80%94%20like%20paparazzi%20or%20fans%20%E2%80%94%20can't%20come%20close.%20Although%20it's%20unclear%20why%20he%20bought%20several%20homes%20on%20Indian%20Creek%20specifically%2C%20privacy%20is%20definitely%20a%20top%20perk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20is%20one%20of%20many%20wealthy%20individuals%20to%20move%20to%20the%20island%2C%20and%20his%20mansions%20have%20raised%20property%20values%20drastically.%20Miami-Dade%20County%20property%20records%20show%20his%20%2479%20million%20purchase%20sold%20for%20%2428%20million%20in%202014.%20(It%20was%20listed%20for%20%2485%20million.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20Indian%20Creek%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d5daaa005c4a00183db886%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20Indian%20Creek%20Island.%3Cp%3EChandan%20Khanna%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Bezos%20came%20in%20and%20bought%2011%20and%2012%20Indian%20Creek%20Island%20Road%2C%20those%20are%20both%20tear%20downs%2C%26quot%3B%20Hertzberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that%20sets%20the%20land%20at%20that%20price%20for%20those%20sized%20lots%2C%20those%2080%2C000%20square%20foot%20lots.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-miami-neighbor-property-selling-vacant-plot-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20roughly%2080%2C000-square-foot%20vacant%20lot%3C%2Fa%3E%20neighboring%20Bezos'%20property%20hit%20the%20market%20in%20December%202024%2C%20asking%20for%20%24200%20million%2C%20a%20little%20more%20than%20what%20the%20billionaire%20paid%20for%20the%20two%20lots.%20That's%20the%20Bezos%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIlya%20Reznik%2C%20the%20vacant%20lot's%20listing%20agent%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20sellers%20she's%20spoken%20to%20will%20not%20accept%20less%20than%20what%20Bezos%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHertzberg%20said%20the%20Bezos%20Effect%20has%20spilled%20off%20the%20island%20to%20nearby%20neighborhoods%20like%20Bal%20Harbour%20and%20Surfside%2C%20which%20sits%20just%20across%20the%20water%20from%20Indian%20Creek%20and%20has%20similar%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20her%20son%2C%20Danny%20Hertzberg%2C%20broke%20a%20record%20in%20October%202024%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherealdeal.com%2Fmiami%2F2024%2F09%2F25%2Fsurfside-spec-developers-set-record-with-20m-mansion-sale%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighest%20sale%20in%20Surfside%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20selling%20a%20home%20for%20%2419.7%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22290a999c-f5fd-4957-9874-a0567324ffb0%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift's%20New%20York%20compound%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-house-real-estate-portfolio-nashville-new-york-california-2023-3%23in-2009-at-age-19-swift-made-her-first-major-purchase-a-4000-square-foot-three-bedroom-penthouse-in-the-adelicia-in-nashville-tennessee-for-199-million-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%20owns%3C%2Fa%3E%20multiple%20real%20estate%20properties%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-taylor-swifts-17-million-rhode-island-mansion-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emansions%20in%20Rhode%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Beverly%20Hills%2C%20and%20a%20penthouse%20in%20Nashville.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20Swift%20has%20turned%20her%20properties%20at%20155%20Franklin%20Street%20in%20the%20Tribeca%20neighborhood%20of%20New%20York%20City%20into%20a%20compound%2C%20paying%20a%20total%20of%20%2447.70%20million%20for%20privacy%2C%20square%20footage%2C%20and%20the%20status%20that%20comes%20with%20living%20in%20one%20of%20the%20cit