e%20turned%20off%20by%20Swift's%20presence%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20since%20celebrities%20live%20all%20over%20Manhattan%3B%20it's%20part%20of%20the%20city's%20culture%20for%20many%20New%20Yorkers%20to%20see%20stars%20day-to-day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20also%20told%20BI%20that%20Swift's%20compound%20is%20comparable%20to%20similar%20listings%20in%20the%20area.%20For%20instance%2C%20Black%20is%20listing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstreeteasy.com%2Fbuilding%2F111-murray-street%2Fpenthouse-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epenthouse%20in%20111%20Murray%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20modern%20luxury%20development%2C%20for%20%2433.95%20million.%20And%20just%20before%20the%20New%20Year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fserhant.com%2Fproperties%2F67-franklin-street-unit-pha-newyorkcity-ny-10013-prch-7711649%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epenthouse%20of%2067%20Franklin%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20luxury%20building%20just%20a%20few%20blocks%20down%20from%20Swift's%20compound%2C%20was%20put%20under%20contract%20for%20%2412%20million%20in%20a%20deal%20by%20real-estate%20agent%20Krista%20Nickols%20of%20SERHANT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Swift's%20presence%20in%20the%20building%20garners%20attention%2C%20with%20paparazzi%20and%20fans%20often%20lining%20the%20streets%20outside%20when%20she%20is%20spotted%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20even%20those%20with%20more%20sinister%20intentions.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F02%2F09%2Fmetro%2Ftaylor-swifts-accused-stalker-avoids-criminal-charges-moved-to-ny-state-mental-hospital%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E33-year-old%20man%20was%20arrested%20three%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202024%20for%20trying%20to%20access%20Swift's%20compound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift's%20stalker%20is%20arrested%20outside%20her%20Tribeca%20apartment%20in%20January%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20s