rk%20Zuckerberg.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Zalubowski%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fmark-zuckerberg-inside-hawaii-compound%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20Wired%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20compound%20was%20built%20in%20secrecy%20and%20includes%20a%205%2C000-square-foot%20underground%20shelter.%20The%20below-ground%20dwelling%20screams%20doomsday%20bunker%2C%20but%20Zuckerberg%20recently%20tried%20to%20quell%20concerns%20from%20locals%20and%20said%20it's%20a%20shelter%20to%20protect%20against%20hurricanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20just%20like%20a%20little%20shelter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Bloomberg.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20basement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKauai%20real-estate%20broker%20Michael%20Ambrose%20told%20BI%20that%20even%20though%20bunkers%20aren't%20that%20common%2C%20Zuckerberg%20isn't%20the%20first%20to%20buy%20land%20in%20Hawaii.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20this%20lady%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%3B%20she%20owns%20like%20a%20hundred%20and%20something%20acres%20out%20here%2C%20and%20she's%20literally%20just%20sitting%20on%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20worth%20millions%20of%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20more%20that%20the%20world%20population%20grows%2C%20the%20more%20there's%20an%20interest%20in%20owning%20physical%20areas%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225232%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kauai%2C%20Hawaii%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5640df74bd86ef195c8bd41b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223488%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKauai%2C%20Hawaii.%3Cp%3EShutterstock%2FPierre%20Leclerc%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Zuckerberg%20resetting%20the%20market%2C%20Ambrose%20said%20several%20billionaires%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-larry-ellison-lanai-hawaii-plans-sustainability-tourism-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20Oracle%20cofounder%20Larry%20Ellison%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20already%20in%20Hawaii%20and%20may%20have%20contributed.%20Still%2C%20his%20presence%20can%20be%20felt%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSay%20you%20could%20be%20neighbors%20with%20the%20richest%20guy%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20clearly%2C%20the%20land%20itself%20has%20more%20value%20because%20of%20the%20next-door%20neighbor%20being%20who%20he%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Ambrose%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmbrose%2C%20for%20example%2C%20highlighted%20a%20vacant%20lot%20for%20sale%20in%20Kilauea%2C%20a%20community%20on%20the%20northern%20shore%20of%20Kauai%20that%20shot%20up%20in%20price%20after%20Zuckerberg%20moved%20in.%20As%20of%20December%202024%2C%20it's%20listed%20for%20%2416.5%20million.%20According%20to%20Zillow%2C%20the%207.87-acre%20lot%20went%20on%20the%20market%20in%202014%20for%20only%20%243.9%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaires-real-estate-compound-privacy-status-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735897021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67740effca1058716a5edc3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaires-real-estate-compound-privacy-status-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Billionaires%20like%20Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20are%20creating%20compounds%20for%20themselves%2C%20purchasing%20multiple%20real%20estate%20properties%20in%20the%20same%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy%2CSamantha%20Grindell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A105%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaires-real-estate-compound-privacy-status-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jennifer