ef%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-more-than-parents-help-with-bills-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735896601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a7c44ba0fc5856d59844d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-more-than-parents-help-with-bills-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Viviana%20Vazquez%20grew%20up%20poor%20and%20now%20earns%20over%20%24150%2C000%20a%20year.%20She%20writes%20about%20struggling%20with%20resentment%20while%20wanting%20to%20give%20back%20to%20her%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Viviana%20Vazquez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-more-than-parents-help-with-bills-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCould%20Have%20Built%20Sheeshmahal%20For%20Myself%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Jabs%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20inaugurated%201%2C675%20flats%20for%20'Jhuggi%20-%20Jhopri'%20(JJ)%20clusters%20and%20two%20urban%20redevelopment%20projects%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20today.%20The%20inauguration%20also%20saw%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20country%20knows%20it%20well%20that%20Modi%20never%20built%20a%20home%20for%20himself%20but%20has%20built%20more%20than%204%20crore%20houses%20for%20the%20poor%3B%20'mai%20bhi%20koi%20sheeshmahal%20bana%20sakta%20tha'%20(even%20I%20could%20have%20built%20a%20Sheeshmahal)%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20at%20the%20event%2C%20alluding%20to%20recent%20allegations%20of%20exorbitant%20expenditures%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20statement%20referred%20to%20an%20October%20inventory%20released%20by%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20(PWD)%2C%20detailing%20high-end%20appliances%20and%20gadgets%20reportedly%20worth%20over%20crores%20installed%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20bungalow.%20The%20controversy%20has%20become%20a%20political%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20Delhi%20is%20surrounded%20by%20an%20'aapada'%20(disaster).%20By%20keeping%20Anna%20Hazare%20at%20the%20front%2C%20a%20few%20'kattar%20beimaan'%20(extremely%20dishonest)%20people%20have%20pushed%20Delhi%20towards%20'aapada'.%20'AAP%20aapada%20bankar%20Delhi%20par%20toot%20padi%20hai'%20(AAP%20has%20descended%20as%20a%20calamity%20on%20Delhi)%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20India%20has%20become%20a%20symbol%20of%20political%20and%20economic%20stability.%20This%20role%20of%20India%20will%20strengthen%20even%20more%20in%202025.%20This%20year%20will%20be%20the%20year%20to%20strengthen%20India's%20position%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20year%20of%20making%20India%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20manufacturing%20centres%20in%20the%20world...%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20his%20X%20handle%2C%20PM%20Modi%20earlier%20said%20this%20was%20an%20important%20day%20for%20Delhi's%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20is%20an%20important%20day%20for%20Delhi's%20development.%20At%20a%20programme%20in%20Ashok%20Vihar%2C%20will%20be%20inaugurating%20and%20laying%20the%20foundation%20stones%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20development%20works%20which%20will%20boost%20'Ease%20of%20Living'%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20of%20newly%20constructed%20flats%20marked%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20second%20successful%20In-Situ%20Slum%20Rehabilitation%20Project%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20handed%20over%20the%20keys%20to%20eligible%20beneficiaries%20of%20EWS%20flats%20at%20Swabhiman%20Apartments%20in%20the%20Ashok%20Vihar%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20spent%20on%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20flat%20by%20the%20central%20government%2C%20the%20eligible%20beneficiaries%20pay%20less%20than%20seven%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20amount%2C%20comprising%20Rs%201.42%20lakh%20as%20a%20nominal%20contribution%20and%20Rs%2030%2C000%20for%20five%20years%20of%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20push%20from%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20comes%20ahead%20of%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Delhi%2C%20expected%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20inaugurated%20two%20urban%20redevelopment%20projects%20--%20the%20World%20Trade%20Centre%20at%20Nauroji%20Nagar%20and%20the%20General%20Pool%20Residential%20Accommodation%20(GPRA)%20Type-II%20quarters%20at%20Sarojini%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20the%20World%20Trade%20Centre%20transformed%20the%20area%20by%20replacing%20more%20than%20600%20dilapidated%20quarters%20with%20state-of-the-art%20commercial%20towers%2C%20offering%20around%2034%20lakh%20square%20feet%20of%20premium%20commercial%20space%20with%20advanced%20amenities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735896480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F6g24co5o_modi_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1-675-flats-2-urban-redevelopment-projects-pm-modis-big-infra-push-in-delhi-7390331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20inaugurated%201%2C675%20flats%20for%20'Jhuggi%20-%20Jhopri'%20(JJ)%20clusters%20and%20two%20urban%20redevelopment%20projects%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1-675-flats-2-urban-redevelopment-projects-pm-