20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-12-13%2Fapple-to-begin-airpods-assembly-in-southern-india-by-early-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirPods%20from%20a%20new%20factory%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20starting%20this%20year%2C%20and%20overseen%20by%20a%20Foxconn%20unit.%20The%20number%20of%20vendors%20in%20Vietnam%20supplying%20Apple%20has%20steadily%20increased%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5f557b8-0b03-4554-9b1b-b9b2f11c76aa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEasier%20said%20than%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224671%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook%20opens%20an%20Apple%20store%20in%20Shanghai%20in%20March.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6621424c10c6b0cde5f0b367%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223114%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChina%20is%20a%20vital%20market%20for%20Apple.%3Cp%3EVCG%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Apple%20has%20been%20taking%20these%20steps%2C%20experts%20believe%20that%20China%20remains%20vital%20to%20Apple's%20operations%20for%20a%20key%20reason%3A%20it's%20not%20yet%20possible%20to%20replicate%20the%20scale%20of%20its%20operations%20in%20the%20country%20elsewhere.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Marah%20said%20that%20much%20of%20Apple's%20success%20in%20China%20has%20come%20down%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bdepth%20of%20the%20engineering%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%26quot%3B%20established%20by%20Cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20established%20a%20deep%20relationship%20with%20suppliers%20that%20involves%20the%20development%20of%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20and%20millions%20of%20identical%20pieces%20of%20machinery%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Marah%20said%2C%20which%20comprise%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20deep%20and%20very%20complex%20bill%20of%20materials%20and%20componentry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimply%20getting%20up%20and%20leaving%20if%20new%20tariffs%20hit%2C%20then%2C%20is%20not%20an%20option.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20picking%20up%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20opportunity%2C%20but%20it'll%20take%20them%20a%20decade%20to%20get%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Marah%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20manufacturing%20expertise%2C%20and%20to%20transfer%20that%20in%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDipanjan%20Chatterjee%2C%20a%20principal%20analyst%20at%20Forrester%2C%20agrees.%20He%20told%20BI%20that%20although%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20way%20yet%20to%20tell%20how%20the%20proposed%20tariffs%20on%20China%20will%20play%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapples-india-push-looks-like-its-paying-off-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboosting%20India's%20manufacturing%20volume%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20face%20of%20tough%20new%20taxes%20on%20China%20won't%20be%20straightforward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20devil%20is%20in%20the%20details%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20India%20will%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20scale%20up%20rapidly%20to%20accommodate%20that%20kind%20of%20additional%20volume%20%E2%80%94%20not%20an%20easy%20task.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20Apple%20will%20proceed%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fchina-welcomes-apples-continued-deeper-presence-2024-10-25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20China's%20commerce%20minister%20Wang%20Wentao%20told%20Cook%20that%20Apple%20is%20%26quot%3Bwelcome%20to%20continue%20deepening%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20Chinese%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook's%20growing%20closeness%20with%20Trump%20over%20the%20years%20may%20offer%20him%20some%20confidence.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20Trump%20planned%20a%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20imports%2C%20Cook%20successfully%20negotiated%20exemptions%20with%20the%20president%20and%20ensured%20Apple's%20su