hallenging%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court's%20decision%20to%20acquit%20Ram%20Rahim%20and%20his%20co-accused%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20noted%20that%20the%20case%20is%20already%20being%20heard%20by%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20Bela%20M%20Trivedi%20and%20the%20matter%20will%20now%20be%20listed%20before%20her%20bench%20for%20further%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2010%2C%202002%2C%20Ranjit%20Singh%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20the%20Khanpur%20Colony%20of%20Haryana's%20Kurukshetra.%20Mr%20Singh's%20murder%20was%20linked%20to%20his%20suspected%20role%20in%20the%20circulation%20of%20an%20anonymous%20letter%20exposing%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20women%20by%20Gurmeet%20Ram%20Rahim%20at%20the%20Dera's%20headquarters%20in%20Sirsa.%20The%20letter%2C%20which%20described%20how%20women%20followers%20were%20being%20abused%2C%20had%20caused%20public%20outcry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20a%20special%20CBI%20court%20in%20Panchkula%20convicted%20Gurmeet%20Ram%20Rahim%20and%20four%20others%20-%20Avtar%20Singh%2C%20Krishan%20Lal%2C%20Jasbir%20Singh%2C%20and%20Sabdil%20Singh%20-%20for%20their%20roles%20in%20the%20murder.%20The%20court%20awarded%20life%20imprisonment%20to%20all%20five%20and%20imposed%20substantial%20fines%3A%20Rs%2031%20lakh%20on%20Ram%20Rahim%2C%20Rs%201.50%20lakh%20on%20Sabdil%20Singh%2C%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20each%20on%20Jasbir%20Singh%20and%20Krishan%20Lal%2C%20and%20Rs%2075%2C000%20on%20Avtar%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20court's%20order%20concluded%20that%20Ram%20Rahim%20orchestrated%20the%20murder%20because%20he%20suspected%20Mr%20Singh's%20involvement%20in%20circulating%20the%20letter%20that%20exposed%20allegations%20of%20rape%20and%20exploitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202024%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20overturned%20the%20CBI%20court's%20conviction%20and%20acquitted%20all%20five%20accused%20in%20the%20Ranjit%20Singh%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Rahim%20had%20appealed%20his%20conviction%20in%20all%20the%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20including%20the%20rape%20cases%20and%20the%20murder%20of%20journalist%20Ram%20Chander%20Chhatarpati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurmeet%20Ram%20Rahim%20Singh's%20conviction%20in%202017%20for%20the%20rape%20of%20two%20women%20followers%20led%20to%20violence%20and%20unrest%20across%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20Delhi.%20The%20violence%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%2030%20people%20and%20injuries%20to%20over%20250.%20The%20Army%20had%20to%20be%20called%20in%20to%20restore%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20rape%20charges%2C%20Ram%20Rahim%20was%20also%20convicted%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20journalist%20Ram%20Chander%20Chhatarpati%2C%20who%20had%20extensively%20reported%20on%20the%20sexual%20assault%20allegations%20against%20the%20Dera%20chief.%20These%20convictions%20resulted%20in%20a%2020-year%20prison%20sentence%20for%20the%20self-styled%20godman.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735891020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fj5oc42go_gurmeet-ram-rahim-singh-youtube_625x300_25_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdera-chief-gurmeet-ram-rahim-gets-top-court-notice-in-2002-murder-case-7390209%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Dera%20Sacha%20Sauda%20chief%20Gurmeet%20Ram%20Rahim%20Singh%20along%20with%20four%20others%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%202002%20murder%20case%20of%20Ranjit%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20Dera%20manager.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdera-chief-gurmeet-ram-rahim-gets-top-court-notice-in-2002-murder-case-7390209%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22De