3A%22How%20To%20Spot%20A%20Lone%20Wolf%20Attacker%3A%20Big%20Challenge%20For%20Anti-Terror%20Agencies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20New%20Year's%20Day%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-says-new-orleans-attacker-acted-alone-had-strong-support-for-isis-7388473%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattack%20in%20the%20US%20city%20of%20New%20Orleans%3C%2Fa%3E%20left%20at%20least%2015%20dead%20and%20dozens%20injured.%20The%20suspect%2C%20identified%20as%20Shamsud-Din%20Jabbar%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20US%20Army%20veteran%2C%20drove%20a%20rented%20pickup%20truck%20into%20a%20crowd.%20Jabbar%2C%20who%20died%20in%20a%20shoot-out%20with%20police%2C%20was%20a%20lone-wolf%20terrorist%20who%20had%20pledged%20allegiance%20to%20the%20terror%20group%20ISIS%20in%20online%20videos%20posted%20just%20hours%20before%20the%20assault%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20five%20videos%20posted%20on%20Jabbar's%20Facebook%20account.%20In%20the%20first%20video%2C%20Jabbar%20said%20he%20originally%20planned%20to%20harm%20his%20family%20and%20friends%20but%20was%20concerned%20that%20the%20news%20headline%20would%20not%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bwar%20between%20the%20believers%20and%20disbelievers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20attack%20marked%20the%20deadliest%20ISIS-inspired%20assault%20on%20US%20soil%20since%20the%202016%20Orlando%20nightclub%20shooting%2C%20which%20saw%2049%20people%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELone-Wolf%20Tactics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Islamic%20State%20has%20not%20officially%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20New%20Orleans%20attack.%20Unlike%20coordinated%20terrorist%20cells%2C%20lone%20wolves%20like%20Jabbar%20operate%20independently%2C%20often%20inspired%20by%20extremist%20propaganda%20disseminated%20online.%20This%20modus%20operandi%20of%20lone%20wolves%20is%20a%20challenge%20to%20traditional%20counterterrorism%20strategies%2C%20which%20rely%20heavily%20on%20infiltrating%20networks%20and%20intercepting%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELone%20offenders%20typically%20employ%20%26quot%3Beasy-access%26quot%3B%20methods%20such%20as%20vehicle%20ramming%2C%20edged%20weapons%2C%20or%20firearms%20to%20inflict%20mass%20casualties.%20The%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%2C%20the%20FBI%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Counterterrorism%20Center%20issued%20a%20bulletin%20on%20December%206%2C%202024%2C%20warning%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20about%20potential%20lone-wolf%20attacks%20during%20the%20holiday%20season.%20Despite%20these%20warnings%2C%20the%20New%20Orleans%20tragedy%20could%20not%20be%20averted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnline%20Extremism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20its%20territorial%20defeat%20in%202019%2C%20ISIS%20has%20shifted%20its%20focus%20to%20the%20digital%20realm%2C%20establishing%20what%20counterterrorism%20experts%20describe%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BDigital%20Caliphate.%26quot%3B%20This%20online%20network%20uses%20social%20media%2C%20encrypted%20messaging%20apps%2C%20and%20dark%20web%20platforms%20to%20radicalise%20individuals%2C%20share%20propaganda%2C%20and%20provide%20tactical%20guidance%20for%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20probing%20the%20New%20Orleans%20attack%20found%20videos%20Jabbar%20posted%20online%20just%20hours%20before%20the%20assault%2C%20pledging%20loyalty%20to%20ISIS%20and%20calling%20for%20violence.%20While%20his%20radicalisation%20process%20remains%20under%20investigation%2C%20early%20findings%20suggest%20he%20may%20have%20been%20influenced%20by%20online%20platforms%20where%20extremist%20content%20flourishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20companies%20have%20made%20strides%20in%20removing%20extremist%20content%2C%20but%20the%20rapid%20migration%20of%20such%20materials%20to%20encrypted%20platforms%20poses%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDomestic%20Radicalisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJabbar%20was%20a%20US%20Army%20veteran%20with%20no%20prior%20known%20ties%20to%20extremist%20networks.%20According%20to%20authorities%2C%20his%20radicalisation%20appeared%20to%20occur%20relatively%20quickly%20and%20was%20likely%20driven%20by%20personal%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20pattern%20mirrors%20other%20recent%20cases%20in%20which%20individuals%20have%20turned%20to%20extremist%20ideologies%20as%20a%20means%20of%20finding%20purpose%20or%20expressing%20anger.%20Islamic%20State-Khorasan%20(IS-K)%2C%20the%20Central%20Asia-based%20affiliate%20of%20ISIS%2C%20has%20been%20particularly%20effective%20in%20leveraging%20online%20platforms%20to%20radicalise%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%2C%20the%20man%20behind%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20July%20last%20year%2C%20acted%20as%20a%20lone%20wolf.%20Crooks%20was%20not%20part%20of%20any%20terror%20group%2C%20neither%20were%20the%20police%20able%20to%20establish%20any%20connection%20between%20him%20and%20extremist%20ideologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20warned%20that%20the%20psychological%20profiles%20of%20lone-actor%20terrorists%20often%20reveal%20a%20combination%20of%20personal%20instability%20and%20ideological%20alignment%20with%20extremist%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735890480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F6inul7v_new-orleans_625x300_02_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-orleans-attack-shamsud-din-jabbar-lone-wolves-and-digital-caliphate-how-individual-actors-pose-challenges-7389943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20New%20Year's%20Day%2C%20an%20attack%20in%20the%20US%20city%20of%20New%20Orleans%20left%20at%20least%2015%20dead%20and%20dozens%20injured.%20The%20suspect%2C%20identified%20as%20Shamsud-Din%20Jabbar%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20US%20Army%20veteran%2C%20drove%20a%20rented%20pickup