0a%20surge%20in%20human%20metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20cases%2C%20sparking%20concerns%20of%20another%20health%20crisis%20after%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20Reports%20and%20social%20media%20posts%20show%20overcrowded%20hospitals%2C%20with%20some%20users%20also%20suggesting%20the%20presence%20of%20multiple%20viruses%20such%20as%20HMPV%2C%20influenza%20A%2C%20Mycoplasma%20pneumoniae%20and%20even%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%20causes%20flu-like%20symptoms%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20severe%20respiratory%20issues%2C%20especially%20among%20children%20and%20vulnerable%20groups.%20Let's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20respiratory%20virus%20in%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20HMPV%2C%20and%20why%20is%20it%20making%20headlines%20in%20China%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%20is%20a%20respiratory%20virus%20that%20causes%20upper%20and%20lower%20respiratory%20infections.%20It%20affects%20individuals%20across%20all%20age%20groups%2C%20with%20young%20children%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20those%20with%20compromised%20immune%20systems%20being%20most%20vulnerable%2C%20according%20to%20CDC.%20It%20was%20first%20identified%20in%202001.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20symptoms%20of%20HMPV%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20symptoms%20of%20HMPV%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20flu%20and%20other%20respiratory%20infections.%20Common%20signs%20include%20cough%2C%20fever%2C%20nasal%20congestion%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath.%20In%20severe%20cases%2C%20the%20virus%20can%20lead%20to%20complications%20like%20bronchitis%20or%20pneumonia.%20The%20incubation%20period%20for%20HMPV%20is%20usually%20between%20three%20and%20six%20days%2C%20with%20symptoms%20lasting%20for%20varying%20durations%20depending%20on%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20infection.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20HMPV%20spread%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%20spreads%20in%20ways%20similar%20to%20other%20respiratory%20viruses.%20Transmission%20occurs%20through%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESecretions%20from%20coughing%20and%20sneezing%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EClose%20personal%20contact%2C%20such%20as%20shaking%20hands%20or%20touching%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETouching%20contaminated%20surfaces%20and%20then%20touching%20the%20mouth%2C%20nose%2C%20or%20eyes%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20most%20at%20risk%20from%20HMPV%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CDC%2C%20HMPV%20poses%20a%20higher%20risk%20to%20certain%20groups%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYoung%20children%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOlder%20adults%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndividuals%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDEWrBg2ydxx%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDEWrBg2ydxx%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDEWrBg2ydxx%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2