s%20to%20others.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20a%20treatment%20or%20vaccine%20for%20HMPV%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20specific%20antiviral%20treatment%20or%20vaccine%20for%20HMPV.%20Medical%20care%20for%20those%20infected%20is%20supportive%2C%20focusing%20on%20alleviating%20symptoms%20and%20preventing%20complications.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20HMPV%20compare%20to%20COVID-19%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%20and%20COVID-19%20share%20many%20similarities%2C%20in%20that%20they%20both%20cause%20respiratory%20issues%20such%20as%20coughing%2C%20fever%2C%20congestion%2C%20sore%20throat%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20and%20both%20spread%20through%20respiratory%20droplets%2C%20according%20to%20WebMD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESevere%20cases%20can%20require%20hospitalisation.%20HMPV%20typically%20peaks%20during%20winter%20and%20spring%2C%20unlike%20COVID-19%2C%20which%20can%20spread%20year-round%20due%20to%20evolving%20variants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudies%20suggest%20HMPV%20cases%20tripled%20in%20some%20regions%20after%20COVID-19%20restrictions%20were%20lifted.%20The%20drop%20in%20exposure%20to%20viruses%20during%20lockdowns%20likely%20weakened%20immunity%2C%20causing%20a%20surge%20in%20respiratory%20infections%20once%20precautions%20were%20relaxed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735888800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fp7kkjuh_covid19_625x300_02_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhmpv-outbreak-in-china-symptoms-spread-and-what-you-should-know-7389007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20is%20witnessing%20a%20surge%20in%20human%20metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20cases%2C%20sparking%20concerns%20of%20another%20health%20crisis%20after%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhmpv-outbreak-in-china-sym