06484.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scottish%20Hiker%20Carrying%20Garmin%20inReach%20GPS%20Device%20Detained%20At%20Delhi%20Airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Scottish%20hiker%20was%20detained%20at%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20on%20Thursday%20for%20carrying%20a%20GPS%20device%2C%20which%20are%20banned%20in%20India.%20Heather%20was%20headed%20to%20Rishikesh%20when%20the%20security%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20handed%20her%20over%20to%20the%20police%20for%20carrying%20a%C2%A0Garmin%20inReach%20GPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeather%20shared%20her%20experience%20on%20Instagram%2C%20asking%20other%20travellers%20not%20to%20bring%20devices%20like%20Garmin%20inReach%20or%20any%20satellite%20communicator%20to%20India.%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20try%20to%20travel%20to%20India%20with%20a%20Garmin%20inReach%20or%20any%20other%20satellite%20communicator%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20her%20post%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20illegal%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20on%20Instagram%2C%20Heather%20said%20that%20she%20even%20contacted%20the%20embassy%20but%20was%20told%20there%20was%20little%20they%20could%20do%20since%20she%20was%20now%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20law%20in%20India.%20Heather%20also%20claimed%20that%20during%20her%20detention%2C%20the%20police%20denied%20her%20access%20to%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20caption%2C%20Heather%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20around%2010.30%20am%2C%20I%20was%20passing%20through%20security%20at%20Delhi%20Airport%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20taking%20an%20internal%20flight%20to%20Rishikesh.%20I%20innocently%20placed%20my%20Garmin%20inReach%20in%20the%20tray%20to%20go%20through%20the%20scanner%2C%20and%20at%20that%20moment%20I%20was%20promptly%20pulled%20aside%20by%20security%20and%20told%20to%20wait.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20after%20being%20made%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20she%20was%20told%20that%20the%20Garmin%20was%20illegal%20in%20India%20%26quot%3Band%20that%20they%20were%20handing%20me%20over%20to%20the%20police.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20eventually%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%20where%20I%20was%20questioned%2C%20in%20a%20fairly%20friendly%20manner%2C%20and%20made%20to%20sign%20document%20after%20document.%20I%20didn't%20take%20the%20'no%20comment'%20stance%2C%20foolishly%20or%20not%2C%20it%20is%20my%20nature%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20and%20after%20all%2C%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20intent%20on%20my%20behalf%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20hours%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20Heather%20said%20she%20was%20released%20around%209%20pm%20but%20was%20told%20she%20would%20have%20to%20return%20for%20a%20court%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20the%20only%20person%20who%20has%20fallen%20victim%20to%20this%20law.%20Hence%2C%20I%20felt%20compelled%20to%20write%20this%20post.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20referenced%20a%20recent%20case%20involving%20a%20Canadian%20runner%20arrested%20in%20India%20in%20December%20for%20carrying%20a%20similar%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Heather%20claimed%20the%20detention%20overwhelmed%20her%2C%20she%20hoped%20sharing%20her%20story%20would%20help%20others%20avoid%20a%20similar%20fate.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20outcome%20will%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20guess%20I%20will%20just%20have%20to%20wait.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20look%20at%20her%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDESjEsxNfBT%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3