in%20China%2C%20there%20are%20complaints%20of%20congested%20hospitals%20and%20overburdened%20healthcare%20systems.%20Health%20experts%20are%20especially%20worried%20about%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20human%20metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%2C%20a%20respiratory%20virus%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20region%20afflicting%20a%20number%20of%20Asian%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20China's%20health%20authorities%2C%20the%20virus%20is%20spreading%20across%20the%20northern%20regions%20of%20the%20country.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0uoQSMTQi6k%5C%22%3EThe%20Chinese%20Center%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20confirmed%20that%20northern%20China%20is%20the%20worst%20affected.%20HMPV%2C%20which%20can%20infect%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20is%20most%20common%20in%20children%2C%20raising%20further%20public%20health%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20social%20media%20reports%20describe%20a%20critical%20situation%2C%20neither%20Chinese%20officials%20nor%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20has%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-faces-new-virus-outbreak-five-years-after-covid-crisis-7385802%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20China%20Faces%20New%20Virus%20Outbreak%20Five%20Years%20After%20Covid%20Crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Vaccine%20Yet%20for%20Virus%20Discovered%2020%20Years%20Ago%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outbreak%20has%20heightened%20awareness%20about%20the%20need%20for%20preventive%20measures%2C%20especially%20since%20no%20vaccine%20exists%20for%20HMPV%20despite%20the%20virus%20being%20known%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20experts%20are%20urging%20vigilance%20and%20adherence%20to%20public%20health%20guidelines%20to%20limit%20the%20virus's%20spread.%20The%20common%20people%20have%20been%20advised%20by%20the%20authorities%20to%20wash%20their%20hands%20and%20wear%20masks%20and%20other%20precautions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20in%20all%20of%20Asia%20are%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20the%20flu%20outbreak%20and%20the%20respiratory%20virus%20spread%20in%20China.%20Regions%20surrounding%20China%20are%20implementing%20strict%20monitoring%20measures.%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20reported%20very%20few%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Japan's%20health%20authorities%20are%20actively%20working%20to%20address%20the%20issue.%20Following%20a%20significant%20influenza%20outbreak%2C%20Japan%20reported%20thousands%20of%20cases%20nationwide%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20local%20media%20on%20Saturday.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnhkworld%2Fen%2Fnews%2F20241220_15%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJapan%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2094%2C259%20flu%20patients%20were%20reported%20in%20one%20week%20leading%20up%20to%20December%2015th%20across%205%2C000%20hospitals%20and%20clinics%20throughout%20the%20country.%20The%20total%20number%20of%20cases%20in%20Japan%20for%20the%20current%20season%20has%20now%20reached%20718%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20HMPV%20virus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.chinacdc.cn%2Fhealth_topics%2Finfectious_diseases%2F202307%2Ft20230719_267896.html%5C%22%3EChinese%20Center%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20(China%20CDC)%20%3C%2Fa%3EHuman%20metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%2C%20belonging%20to%20the%20Pneumoviridae%2C%20Metapneumovirus%20genus%2C%20is%20an%20enveloped%20single-stranded%20negative-sense%20RNA%20virus.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%202001%2C%20it%20was%20first%20detected%20by%20Dutch%20scholars%20in%20nasopharyngeal%20aspirate%20samples%20of%20children%20with%20respiratory%20infections%20caused%20by%20unknown%20pathogens.%20Serological%20studies%20have%20shown%20that%20it%20has%20existed%20for%20at%20least%2060%20years%2C%20being%20distributed%20all%20over%20the%20world%20as%20a%20common%20respiratory%20pathogen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhmpv-outbreak-in-china-symptoms-spread-and-what-you-should-know-7389007%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHMPV%20Outbreak%20In%20China%3A%20Symptoms%2C%20Spread%20And%20What%20You%20Should%20Know%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20fatality%20rate%20of%20HMPV%20infection%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnChildren%2C%20immunocompromised%20populations%20and%20the%20elderly%20are%20susceptible%20and%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20co-infected%20with%20other%20respiratory%20viruses.%20HMPV%20often%20causes%20common%20cold%20symptoms%2C%20manifested%20as%20cough%2C%20fever%2C%20nasal%20congestion%20and%20wheezing%2C%20but%20sometimes%20it%20can%20result%20in%20bronchitis%20and%20pneumonia%20in%20severe%20cases.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20susceptible%20individuals%20with%20underlying%20medical%20conditions%2C%20HMPV%20infection%20can%20lead%20to%20death.%20Based%20on%20data%20from%20an%20article%20published%20in%20Lancet%20Global%20Health%20in%202021%2C%20one%20percent%20of%20acute%20lower%20respiratory%20infection-related%20deaths%20in%20children%20under%20age%20five%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20HMPV.%20Currently%2C%20there%20is%20no%20vaccine%20or%20effective%20medication%20against%20HMPV%2C%20and%20treatment%20is%20mostly%20focused%20on%20alleviating%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735886040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fpoqoq0rg_virus-spread_625x300_03_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fconcerns-rise-as-covid-like-hmpv-virus-spreads-across-asia-7389403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22HMPV%2C%20which%20primarily%20affects%20children%2C%20has%20spread%20