0brigade%20with%20its%20own%20weaponry%2C%20including%2018%20AMX%2010%20armored%20vehicles%2C%2018%20truck-mounted%20Caesar%20howitzers%2C%20and%20128%20armored%20troop%20carriers.%20The%20unit%20also%20fields%20some%20of%20Germany's%20prized%20Leopard%202A4%20main%20battle%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20November%2C%20the%20155th%20was%20set%20to%20hit%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20with%20French%20officials%20saying%20these%20Ukrainian%20troops%20were%20now%20equipped%20to%20fight%20with%20Western%20battlefield%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed3c71fa-e416-41da-8a9f-485629ff76f0%5C%22%3E1%2C700%20desertions%2C%20war%20reporter%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensor.net%2Fua%2Fresonance%2F3528007%2Fdbr-porushylo-spravu-schodo-formuvannya-155-yi-brygady%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20last%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Ukrainian%20journalist%20Yuriy%20Butusov%20said%20the%20brigade%20has%20been%20buckling%20from%20desertion%20and%20leadership%20issues%2C%20even%20before%20it%20was%20deployed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-pokrovsk-offensive-combat-vehicles-losses-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPokrovsk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20brigade%20fired%20the%20first%20shot%2C%201%2C700%20servicemen%20left%20it%20voluntarily%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Butusov.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20provide%20evidence%20for%20his%20claim%2C%20but%20published%20a%20tally%20of%20the%20unit's%20strength%20over%20time%20that%20said%20hundreds%20of%20men%20deserted%20monthly%20from%20March%20to%20November%2C%20forcing%20the%20155th%20to%20keep%20replenishing%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20factor%20in%20the%20desertion%20rate%2C%20Butusov%20wrote%2C%20was%20that%20many%20in%20the%20unit%20had%20been%20forcibly%20recruited%20off%20Ukraine's%20streets.%20About%2050%20men%20also%20went%20AWOL%20while%20the%20unit%20was%20training%20in%20France%2C%20B