%20it%20from%20the%20stupid%20military%20decisions%20of%20our%20generals%20and%20tore%20the%20unit%20apart%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButusov's%20report%20has%20since%20drawn%20outcry%20among%20Ukrainian%20figures%2C%20such%20as%20Lt.%20Col.%20Bohdan%20Krotevych%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20chief%20of%20staff%20in%20the%20Azov%20Brigade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20it's%20sheer%20idiocy%20to%20create%20new%20brigades%20and%20equip%20them%20with%20new%20technology%20while%20existing%20ones%20are%20undermanned%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBohdanKrotevych%2Fstatus%2F1874489196263428544%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerhii%20Sternenko%2C%20a%20well-known%20Ukrainian%20lawyer%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-dronemakers-war-unwinnable-dirt-cheap-crowdfunding-veterans-civilians-russia-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovides%20crowdfunded%20drones%20to%20military%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20his%20organization%20was%20assisting%20the%20155th%20because%20the%20brigade%20lacked%20officially%20provided%20drones%20and%20jammers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20create%20a%20new%20brigade%20when%20existing%20brigades%20are%20critically%20understaffed%2C%20only%20to%20later%20divide%20it%20and%20transfer%20personnel%20to%20the%20old%20brigades%3F%20What's%20the%20point%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fssternenko%2F38186%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20Tuesday%20on%20his%20Telegram%20channel.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brigade's%20fate%20threatens%20to%20mar%20the%20legacy%20of%20Macron's%20efforts%20to%20position%20France%20as%20a%20staunch%20ally%20of%20Ukraine.%20Paris%20has%20pledged%20some%20%243%20billion%20in%20military%20aid%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20and%20Macron%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20European%20leaders%20pushing%20for%20Ukraine's%20accession%20to%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20floated%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-emmanual-macron-france-join-ukraine-war-on-russia-conditions-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esending%20French%20troops%20to%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20Russia%20were%20to%20score%20a%20massive%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226870%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20welcomes%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20at%20the%20Elysee%20Palace%20in%20October.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67776ef359d276c1cdafe0e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224580%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20October%2C%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20visited%20Paris%20for%20the%20fifth%20time%20since%20the%20war%20began.%3Cp%3ERemon%20Haazen%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20and%20Ukrainian%20Defense%20Ministries%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%20by%20BI%2C%20the%20155th%20Mechanized%20Brigade's%20communications%20service%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BUntil%20the%20official%20investigation%20is%20completed%2C%20the%20brigade%20commander%20will%20not%20provide%20any%20comments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BAnne%20of%20Kyiv%26quot%3B%20brigade%20is%20just%20one%20of%20several%20training%20projects%20that%20France%20and%20Europe%20have%20been%20working%20on%20with%20Ukraine.%20Since%20late%202022%2C%20over%2063%2C000%20Ukrainian%20troops%20have%20been%20trained%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F11%2F08%2Fukraine-council-extends-the-mandate-of-the-eu-military-assistance-mission-for-two-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEuropean%20Union