0years%2C%20with%202%2C42%2C334%20births%20marking%20a%203.1%25%20increase%20over%20the%20previous%20year.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20country's%20total%20population%20has%20been%20declining%20since%202020.%20Additionally%2C%20South%20Korea%20has%20become%20a%20super-aged%20society%2C%20with%2020%25%20of%20its%20population%20aged%2065%20and%20older.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwith-242334-newborn-babies-in-2024-south-korea-records-rise-in-birthrate-after-nine-years%2Farticleshow%2F116904143.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwith-242334-newborn-babies-in-2024-south-korea-records-rise-in-birthrate-after-nine-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F116904143.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwith-242334-newborn-babies-in-2024-south-korea-records-rise-in-birthrate-after-nine-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F116904143.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20120%20Elite%20Israeli%20Forces%20Raided%20Syria%2C%20Destroyed%20Missile%20Plant%20In%203%20Hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20on%20Thursday%20declassified%20details%20of%20a%20high-stakes%20operation%20in%20which%20120%20Israeli%20commandos%20raided%20and%20destroyed%20an%20alleged%20underground%20Iran-funded%20missile%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Syria.%20The%20mission%2C%20codenamed%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Many%20Ways%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20carried%20out%20on%20September%208%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BDeep%20Layer%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20allegedly%20located%20near%20the%20Masyaf%20area%20in%20western%20Syria%2C%20a%20region%20considered%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Syrian%20air%20defences.%20Israeli%20officials%20claimed%20that%20the%20site%2C%20a%20flagship%20project%20of%20Iran's%20missile%20production%20program%2C%20was%20intended%20to%20supply%20precision%20missiles%20to%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20to%20the%20Assad%20regime%20in%20Syria.%20The%20operation%20was%20carried%20out%20without%20injuries%20to%20the%20Israeli%20forces%2C%20the%20officials%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Facility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IAF%2C%20Iran's%20construction%20of%20the%20Deep%20Layer%20facility%20began%20in%20late%202017%2C%20following%20an%20earlier%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20an%20aboveground%20rocket%20engine%20manufacturing%20site%20at%20the%20Scientific%20Studies%20and%20Research%20Center%20(CERS)%20in%20Jamraya%2C%20southern%20Syria.%20This%20attack%20led%20Iran%20to%20shift%20its%20operations%20underground%2C%20aiming%20to%20safeguard%20its%20missile%20production%20capabilities%20from%20future%20airstrikes.%20By%202021%2C%20the%20underground%20facility%2C%20buried%2070%20to%20130%20metres%20into%20a%20mountain%2C%20had%20become%20operational%2C%20with%20missile%20production%20capabilities%20nearing%20full%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ftgoh1gtg_iaf-mission-_625x300_03_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video%20posted%20on%20X%20by%20%40IDF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20horseshoe-shaped%20structure%20featured%20three%20primary%20entrances%3A%20one%20for%20raw%20materials%2C%20another%20for%20completed%20missiles%2C%20and%20a%20third%20for%20logistics%20and%20office%20access.%20Sixteen%20production%20rooms%20lined%20the%20facility%2C%20including%20mixers%20for%20rocket%20fuel%2C%20missile%20body%20construction%20areas%2C%20and%20paint%20rooms.%20The%20IDF%20estimated%20the%20facility's%20annual%20output%20could%20have%20ranged%20between%20100%20and%20300%20missiles%2C%20capable%20of%20reaching%20targets%20up%20to%20300%20kilometres%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrategically%20located%20just%20200%20km%20north%20of%20the%20Israeli%20border%20and%2045%20km%20from%20Syria's%20western%20coastline%2C%20the%20Deep%20Layer%20facility%20offered%20Iran%20a%20means%20of%20circumventing%20Israeli%20strikes%20on%20overland%20weapons%20convoys%20to%20Hezbollah.%20The%20underground%20site%20would%20have%20enabled%20Hezbollah%20to%20receive%20missiles%20directly%20from%20Syria's%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Prep%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF's%20decision%20to%20raid%20the%20facility%20came%20after%20years%20of%20monitoring%20and%20intelligence%20gathering.%20While%20initial%20plans%20were%20formulated%20years%20prior%2C%20the%20operation%20gained%20urgency%20amid%20the%20multifront%20war%20that%20began%20in%20October%202023%2C%20involving%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20other%20Iran-backed%20militias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDECLASSIFIED%3A%20In%20September%202024%2C%20before%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Assad%20Regime%2C%20our%20soldiers%20conducted%20an%20undercover%20operation%20to%20dismantle%20an%20Iranian-funded%20underground%20precision%20missile%20production%20site%20in%20Syria.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWatch%20exclusive%20footage%20from%20this%20historic%20moment.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fs0bTDNwx77%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fs0bTDNwx77%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(%40IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIDF%2Fstatus%2F1874849694012309593%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%202%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elite%20Shaldag%20unit%2C%20known%20for%20long-range%20penetration%20operations%2C%20and%20Unit%20669%2C%20specialising%20in%20combat%20search%20and%20rescue%2C%20were%20selected%20for%20the%20mission.%20Over%20two%20months%20of%20intensive%20training%20included%20simulations%20and%20backup%20scenarios%20to%20mitigate%20risks%20during%20the%20high-stakes%20operation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mission%20date%20was%20chosen%20for%20its%20favourable%20weather%20conditions.%20Extensive%20intelligence%20efforts%20mapped%20the%20facility's%20layout%2C%20identified%20Syrian%20air%20defence%20capabilities%2C%20and%20analysed%20potential%20threats%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Execution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20began%20with%20100%20Shaldag%20commandos%20and%2020%20Unit%20669%20medics%20boarding%20four%20CH-53%20%26quot%3BYasur%26quot%3B%20heavy%20transport%20helicopters.%20Escorted%20by%20AH-64%20attack%20helicopters%2C%2021%20fighter%20jets%2C%20five%20drones%2C%20and%2014%20reconnaissance%20planes%2C%20the%20convoy%20departed%20from%20Israel%2C%20flying%20over%20the%20Mediterranean%20to%20avoid%20Syrian%20radar%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20reaching%20Syrian%20airspace%2C%20the%20helicopters%20flew%20exceptionally%20low%20to%20evade%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20densest%20air%20defence%20zones%2C%20second%20only%20to%20Damascus.%20To%20mask%20the%20commandos'%20approach%2C%20IAF%20aircraft%20launched%20diversionary%20strikes%20on%20other%20Syrian%20targets%2C%20drawing%20attention%20away%20from%20the%20Masyaf%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20helicopters%20landed%20near%20the%20facility's%20entrances%2C%20deploying%20troops%20while%20maintaining%20a%20defensive%20perimeter.%20Unit%20669%20personnel%20remained%20on%20standby%20aboard%20the%20aircraft%2C%20prepared%20to%20evacuate%20or%20treat%20casualties%20if%20necessary.%20A%20surveillance%20drone%20launched%20by%20the%20commandos%20monitored%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp