%20or%20else%20the%20fish%20won%E2%80%99t%20thrive.%20Given%20that%20we%20were%20making%20artificial%20ponds%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20use%20these%20to%20help%20the%20fish%20grow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20emphasising%20the%20care%20he%20took%20to%20ensure%20his%20farm%E2%80%99s%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adjusting%20his%20approach%2C%20he%20also%20found%20that%20combining%20crops%20like%20turmeric%2C%20banana%2C%20and%20oranges%2C%20and%20selling%20cultured%20fish%2C%20all%20together%2C%20could%20yield%20better%20results.%20For%20each%20pond%20(approximately%200.4%20acres)%2C%20he%20can%20generate%20up%20to%20Rs%201.6%20lakh%20in%20revenue%2C%20yielding%20a%20Rs%201%20lakh%20profit.%20In%20addition%20to%20fish%2C%20crop%20cultivation%20in%20and%20around%20the%20ponds%20generates%20around%20Rs%2070%2C000%20in%20spending%20and%20a%20Rs%201%20lakh%20profit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20importance%20of%20education%20and%20community%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Sarbeswar%E2%80%99s%20core%20beliefs%20is%20the%20importance%20of%20education%20in%20farming.%20He%20stresses%20the%20role%20of%20young%2C%20educated%20individuals%20in%20modernising%20agriculture.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20days%2C%20young%20people%20are%20very%20innovative%20and%20active.%20I%20want%20to%20encourage%20these%20well-read%20individuals%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284854%2Ftelangana-man-converts-ancestral-land-into-forest-environment-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20into%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20use%20tried%20and%20tested%2C%20scientifically%20backed%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20He%20believes%20that%20while%20traditional%20farming%20methods%20have%20served%20their%20purpose%2C%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20enough%20to%20achieve%20the%20best%20results%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20ever-changing%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class