div%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20works%20in%20multiple%20verticals%20like%20education%2C%20skill%20development%20and%20entrepreneurship%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20benefit%20of%20children%2C%20women%2C%20youngsters%2C%20and%20bonded%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EOver%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Sahyog%20has%20collaborated%20closely%20with%20governmental%20departments%20to%20conduct%20148%20successful%20missions%2C%20rescuing%20more%20than%202%2C788%20children%20(2%2C065%20boys%20and%20723%20girls)%20from%20exploitation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20focuses%20on%20liberating%20victims%20and%20reintegrating%20them%20into%20society%20through%20counselling%2C%20education%2C%20and%20skill%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGenerations%20lost%3A%20The%20hidden%20scars%20of%20child%20labour%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVulnerable%20individuals%2C%20especially%20from%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20can%20be%20trapped%20in%20exploitative%20debt%20cycles%2C%20frequently%20small%20and%20fabricated.%20This%20forces%20families%20to%20send%20their%20children%20to%20work%20as%20labourers%20to%20repay%20the%20debt%2C%20perpetuating%20a%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20and%20exploitation%2C%20Shekhar%20informs.%20Alarmingly%2C%20many%20child%20labourers%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20estimated%20at%2010.1%20million%20by%20the%20International%20Labour%20Organisation%20(ILO)%20%E2%80%94%20are%20forced%20to%20work%20in%20extremely%20hazardous%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChildren%20are%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F320999%2Fdr-shankar-nath-jha-educates-children-from-bihar-musahar-community-prevents-child-marriage-labour%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20cheap%20labour%20for%20factory%3C%2Fa%3E%20owners.%20They%20are%20in%20a%20vulnerable%20position%20where%20they%20do%20not%20voice%20their%20opinions%20or%20difficulties%20like%20adults.%20Moreover%2C%20parents%20are%20under%20the%20assumption%20that%20their%20child%20is%20working%20in%20a%20safe%20environment%20and%20getting%20three%20meals%20a%20day.%20Despite%20the%20struggle%2C%20the%20child%20continues%20to%20work%20thinking%20that%20their%20family%20is%20receiving%20the%20monetary%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Harish%20Kumar%2C%20the%20rescue%20and%20rehabilitation%20manager%20at%20Sahyog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20father%20of%20two%20daughters.%20Whenever%20I%20look%20at%20these%20children%20suffering%20under%20harsh%20circumstances%20due%20to%20financial%20downfall%20and%20illiteracy%2C%20I%20think%20of%20my%20children%20and%20how%20I%20would%20feel%20if%20such%20a%20situation%20arose%20in%20my%20family.%20Sometimes%20it%20becomes%20difficult%20to%20sleep%20as%20I%20am%20reminded%20of%20the%20difficult%20childhood%20the%20children%20are%20experiencing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1734543001.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Child%20labourers%20working%20in%20unsafe%20conditions%20for%20prolonged%20hours.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1734543001.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1734543001-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1734543001-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1734543001-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1734543001-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390686%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChild%20labourers%20working%20in%20unsafe%20conditions%20for%20prolonged%20hours.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWhile%20the%20number%20of%20children%20rescued%20varies%20from%20mission%20to%20mission%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%2070%2C%20and%20other%20times%20as%20few%20as%20two%20%E2%80%94%20each%20successful%20rescue%20brings%20them%20closer%20to%20creating%20a%20safe%20and%20comfortable%20environment%20for%20vulnerable%20children.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20missions%20are%20not%20devoid%20of%20setbacks%20and%20challenges.%20Shekhar%20recalls%20an%20incident%20when%20the%20organisation%20received%20information%20regarding%20a%20bonded%20labourer%20of%2012%20to%2013%20years%20old%3B%20he%20was%20being%20pressured%20to%20work%20overtime%20with%20a%20steel-cutting%20machine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20filed%20the%20complaint%20and%20completed%20the%20pre-rescue%20meeting%2C%20and%20we%20were%20supposed%20to%20conduct%20the%20rescue%20mission%20around%2011%20am.%20I%20was%20disheartened%20when%20I%20found%20out%20that%20the%20child%20had%20lost%20two%20fingers%20at%2010%3A30%20am%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20I%20consider%20this%20a%20failure%20as%20if%20we%20had%20gone%2030%20minutes%20before%2C%20and%20we%20could%20have%20saved%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20fingers%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Shekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20the%20future%3A%20Rescue%20and%20rehabilitation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20crucial%20role%20NGOs%20play%2C%20Harish%20informs%20that%20the%20complete%20details%20regarding%20the%20factories%2C%20workers%2C%20etc%2C%20are%20provided%20by%20the%20team%20involved%20in%20the%20recce%20and%20investigation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20impact%20of%20a%20rescue%20mission%20and%20the%20pressure%20built%20creates%20fear%20among%20other%20factory%20owners%20to%20not%20be%20involved%20in%20such%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shekhar%20adds.%20Following%20a%20tip-off%20from%20the%20workers%20or%20the%20society%2C%20the%20NGO%20initiates%20the%20identification%20process%20by%20having%20its%20members%20examine%20the%20area%20thoroughly%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20assess%20factories%2C%20identifying%20factors%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263730%2Findia-abandoned-child-homeless-rescue-jobs-ngo-free-food-shelter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20child%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20tasks%2C%20working%20conditions%2C%20and%20any%20instances%20of%20physical%20or%20mental%20exploitation%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Harish.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20areas%20like%20Wazirpur%2C%20industrialists%20are%20highly%20vigilant%20with%20constant%20CCTV%20surveillance%2C%20prompting%20the%20rescue%20team%20to%20often%20resort%20to%20undercover%20tactics%2C%20entering%20factories%20disguised%20as%20workers.%20The%20entry%20and%20exit%20of%20vehicles%20during%20the%20mission%20is%20mapped%20to%20perfection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20gathering%20the%20necessary%20evidence%2C%20a%20written%20complaint%20is%20filed%20with%20the%20Sub-Divisional%20Magistrate%20(SDM).%20Subsequently%2C%20a%20pre-rescue%20meeting%20is%20convened%20by%20the%20SDM%20or%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20(DM)%2C%20bringing%20together%20representatives%20from%20various%20departments%2C%20including%20labour%2C%20revenue%2C%20police%2C%20medical%2C%20and%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rescue%20mission%20is%20done%20where%20multiple%20Government%20departments%20are%20involved%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390690%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rescue%20mission%20is%20done%20where%20multiple%20Government%20departments%20are%20involved.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20SOP%20demands%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20rescue%20mission%2048%20hours%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20departments%20and%20the%20availability%20of%20the%20SDM%20sometimes%20delays%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shekhar%20admits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20are%20the%20facilitators%20for%20the%20rescue%20mission%2C%20we%20become%20the%20witness%20for%20the%20same.%20The%20Government%20deals%20with%20proper%20documentation%20of%20the%20details.%20All%20the%20FIR%20copies%20are%20maintained%20by%20us%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20conducted%20and%20upcoming%20missions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20date%20and%20time%20for%20the%20rescue%20mission%20are%20fixed%20without%20revealing%20details%20like%20the%20address%20and%20factory%20name%20to%20avoid%20external%20hurdles%20and%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20political%20pressure%20and%20involvement%20of%20goons%20makes%20the%20rescue%20tricky%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shekhar.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20get%20threats%20via%20calls%20and%20messages%3B%20we%20also%20have%20been%20harmed%20and%20threatened%20earlier.%20To%20avoid%20this%2C%20we%20request%20an%20additional%20police%20force%20and%20take%20them%20during%20the%20rescue%20to%20handle%20the%20situation%20effectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20successful%20rescue%2C%20the%20children%20undergo%20a%20thorough%20medical%20examination%20to%20assess%20for%20signs%20of%20abuse%2C%20physical%20and%20mental%2C%20and%20other%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20exposure%20to%20hazardous%20factories%20like%20coating%2C%20steel%2C%20utensils%2C%20embroidery%2C%20and%20the%20like.%20%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20sexual%20abuse%20remains%20a%20significant%20concern%2C%20particularly%20for%20girls%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shekhar%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%20subsequently%20places%20the%20children%20in%20Child%20Care%20Institutes%20(CCIs)%20for%20rehabilitation%20until%20they%20can%20be%20reunited%20with%20their%20families.%20Comprehensive%20counselling%20is%20provided%20for%20both%20the%20children%20and%20their%20parents%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20into%20the%20vicious%20circle%20of%20bonded%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20these%20children%20are%20not%20given%20the%20wages%20for%20the%2